    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">328 Mickle Street</name>
                    <name type="place">Camden New Jersey</name>
                    <date when="1887-04-21">April 21 '87</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear C W E</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Yours came this forenoon, &#38; was read &#38; reread, &#38; dispatched on the round
                to Kennedy,<ptr target="n3039"/> John Burroughs,<ptr target="n0129"/> &#38; Dr.
                    Bucke<ptr target="n0119"/>&#8212;all so anxious to get definite news from
                William.<ptr target="n2002"/> It somehow seems the most encouraging yet&#8212;God grant our dear friend
                may indeed get complete recovery&#8212;Write often as you can, dear friend. With me
                &#38; my affairs no great ripple&#8212;I am worldlily comfortable &#38; in good
                physical condition as usual of late&#8212;I went on to New York&#8212;was convoyed
                by my dear old Quaker friend R Pearsall Smith<ptr target="n4979"/>&#8212;had a
                success at the lecture 14th<ptr target="yal.00238_n3"/> (netted $600 for my self&#8212;Andrew Carnegie<ptr
                    target="loc.03486_n1"/> gave $350 for his box)&#8212;had a stunning <hi
                    rend="italic">reception</hi>&#8212;I think 300 people, many ladies&#8212;that
                evn'g Westminster Hotel&#8212;newspapers friendly, everybody friendly even the
                authors&#8212;&#38; returned here Friday 4 p m train from N Y. in good
                order&#8212;Am going over to Phila: this p m to be sculp'd by St Gaudiens, the N Y
                sculptor<ptr target="tex.00466_n1"/> who has come on, to do it&#8212;Signs of spring rather late, but
                here&#8212;I am call'd to dinner (baked shad)&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
